**@config** — Specify a Tailwind config file for this CSS file.
```css
@config './tailwind.config.js';
```
Useful in multi-config setups.

**theme()** — Reference design tokens in CSS.
```css
.element {
  color: theme('colors.blue.500');
  padding: theme('spacing.4');
}
```
Accesses values from your Tailwind config.

**screen()** — Reference breakpoints in @media.
```css
@media screen(md) {
  .element { display: flex; }
}
```
Resolves to the breakpoint value from your config.
